data.description: BACK ON THE MARKET!  HIGHLY QUALIFIED BUYER MYSTERIOUSLY BECAME UNQUALIFIED.  LOCATION-LOCATION-LOCATION!  Super Clean 1.5 Story Sandwiched Between Preston Road and The North Dallas Tollway.  Outstanding Features Include: 4 Downstairs Bedrooms; Big Bonus Room Upstairs That's Ideal For A Kids Play Room or For Watching Football on Saturday & Sunday;  Freshly Painted; Recently Updated Vinyl Flooring; Outstanding Curb Appeal With Recently Installed Zoysia Grass and Updated BOB Fence.  Walking Distance To Rogers Elementary, Staley Middle School, & Warren Park.  Warren park has trails,pond,volleyball,basketball & Tennis courts,football, baseball+soccer fields,playground and picnic area . NO PIDS-NO MUDS!  Buyer To Verify All Information.
